-- Hardy Oil Says it Agrees to Sell Nigerian Business to Inergia Petroleum
-- B y   L o u i s a   F a h y
-- 2010-09-21T06:09:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/hardy-oil-says-ot-agrees-to-sell-nigerian-business-to-inergia-petroleum.html
Hardy Oil and Gas Plc said today it
entered an agreement to sell its wholly-owned Nigerian business
for $4.55 million to Inergia Petroleum Ltd., a new  upstream
energy company focused on Nigeria. 